• View your games in extremely sharp clarity on the large, 24.5-inch, VA panel with its FHD resolution;
• Experience unparalleled smoothness in all your games on the 280Hz Legion R25f-30;
• Stay a step ahead of the competition with ultra-responsive gameplay supported by 0.5ms MPRT response times;
• Game without any stutter or motion blur thanks to AMD FreeSync™ Premium and the ClearMR 7000 certification;
Powers high visual fidelity gaming;
• The color of all your game visuals pops on the display with its 99% sRGB and 90% DCI-P3 color space coverage;
• Lighting and shadows in your games look super realistic on the HDR-supported monitor;
• Get situational awareness while you game with rich, stereo sound pumped out by the two, 3W speakers;
Helps you game for hours;
• Comfortably game for hours using the LTPS (Lift, Tilt, Pivot, Swivel) stand to precisely adjust the monitor to suit your preferred seating position;
• Avoid eye strain while gaming with Lenovo’s Natural Low Blue Light technology which reduces harmful blue light without any color distortion;
• The gaming tools supported by Lenovo Artery software let you get a leg up on the competition in any game you play.
